{"tid":649761,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"洛賓：球證沒有偏幫皇馬","createTime":"2018-05-01T20:41:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T04:36:23.000Z","uid":9581,"like":104,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ada67ec1e685b9ae90048bb738a89e29e1a12b11","tid":649761,"uid":9581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T20:41:00.000Z","msg":"於今夜歐聯4強次回合，拜仁翼鋒洛賓因傷未隨隊作客馬德里。完場時記者在慕尼黑找到荷蘭人，被問道球證在場上的表現，洛賓表示：「球證沒有對皇馬做成得益。拜仁根本不存在反勝的機會。」<br />\n<br />\n記者問到洛賓傷勢看來並不嚴重，為何不隨隊作戰，拜仁翼鋒表示：「我已經只餘下一粒，我怕我在禁區被踢爆另一粒，也不能換取對方一個十二碼，我怕了，我不打了。」<br />\n<br />\n記者又問題對球隊有何評價，洛賓說︰「沒有，甚麼都沒有，這場本來就不可能勝出的賽事，我的朋友們已經做得不錯，我本來就沒有期望過，我一直都只等待明天iris的演出。」<br />\n<br />\n記者又問到，面對那樣的球證荷蘭人會否感到憤怒，他說︰「憤怒值能大於金錢嗎? 」<br />\n<br />\n記者想再問時，洛賓說他要休息，要留精神看明天iris的演出，並叫大家用TVB Anywhere看香港星期一至五晚上8時播放的《愛回家．開心速遞》"},{"pid":"bc40de22d2246d5badb1fe65a2fd1eaaba25353b","tid":649761,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T20:42:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1179827e0ab8367b28013ee8c57899180a470c0b","tid":649761,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T20:42:14.000Z","msg":"手足冷靜少少一個夠喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"255771bd4787eac2967c7bda89d9ede24014177e","tid":649761,"uid":110761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T20:43:14.000Z","msg":"泥明顯半場打定  完場即po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361006120147d9d820a42aacb9cb76b82f631b4b","tid":649761,"uid":99960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T20:43:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"